{"id":115244,"type":2,"name":"Gone Nutty","name_cn":"消失的松果","date":"2002-11-28","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/5c/2a/115244_E001M.jpg","rating":{"rank":3508,"total":59,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":1,"4":2,"5":4,"6":21,"7":25,"8":5,"9":1,"10":0},"score":6.5},"summary":"　　无尽冰原，寂静无声。松鼠斯克莱特（Scrat）找到一枚坚果，他欢欢喜喜地穿过冰原，爬上了一棵巨大的树干。这棵树早已拦腰折断，空洞的树心成为斯克莱特最好的仓库。如今这里已经密密麻麻塞满了坚果，斯克莱特始终无法将新采来的坚果塞入其中，甚至因为过于用力还导致整个坚果堆崩溃。成百上千的坚果从树干中如潮水般喷涌而出，裹挟着斯克莱特跌落悬崖。多年的心血怎能功亏一篑？即使在坠落过程中斯克莱特也全然不顾个鼠安危，奋力搜集着每一枚坚果。执着如斯，殊为难得…… \r\n　　本片为动画片《冰河世纪》的配套短片。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>消失的松果</li><li><span>话数: </span>1</li><li><span>执行制片人: </span><a href=\"/person/45620\">Chris Wedge</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>消失的橡果</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>消失的坚果</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Scrat's Missing Adventure</li><li><span>上映年度: </span>2002-11-28</li><li><span>片长: </span>5分钟</li><li><span>类型: </span>喜剧 / 短片</li><li><span>制片国家/地区: </span>美国</li><li><span>语言: </span>无对白</li><li><span>IMDb链接: </span>tt0342965</li><li><span>导演: </span>卡洛斯·沙尔丹哈</li><li><span>编剧: </span>William H. Frake III / Dan Shefelman</li><li><span>主演: </span>Chris Wedge</li>","collection":{"on_hold":2,"dropped":3,"wish":4,"collect":96,"doing":1},"tags":[{"name":"短片","count":23},{"name":"欧美","count":19},{"name":"2002","count":15},{"name":"美国","count":12},{"name":"搞笑","count":8},{"name":"3D","count":4},{"name":"治愈","count":3},{"name":"欢乐","count":2},{"name":"其它","count":1},{"name":"2002年","count":1},{"name":"童年","count":1},{"name":"动画","count":1},{"name":"剧场版","count":1},{"name":"","count":""}],"eps":[{"id":437579,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/437579","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":""}],"crt":[{"id":89053,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/crt/l/e9/16/89053_crt_8jROx.jpg","name":"Scrat","desc":"Chris Wedge"}],"staff":[{"id":45620,"image":"","name":"Chris Wedge","desc":"执行制片人"}],"relations":[{"id":40190,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/cb/d3/40190_4Vy1o.jpg